1300.name: L-Ag45Sn
1300.Applications:
Brazing a weight range of different metals in maintanance and repair with excelent strenght, Boiler making, tubing, cooling equipment etc.
Do not use this alloy above working temperatures of 200ºC
1300.Suitable_For: Steels, Copper, Copper alloys, Stainless steel, Cast Iron, Nickel and Nickel alloys. Also suitable for dissimilar joints between these metals.
